  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd-\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1-\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd-70-\u0b90-\u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f-\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1/175-299271",
  "time_ut": 1656277947,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 70% \u0b90  \u0bae\u0bc2\u0b9f \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Decided to close 70% of gas stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Gas Station Owners' Association says it has temporarily closed 70% of gas stations islandwide due to fuel shortages in the country.",
        "The association has been urging people not to wait in line as there is not enough fuel available even though it was booked 30 days in advance.",
        "According to the association, only 20 per cent of the people have difficulty in distributing fuel as only a small amount of fuel is distributed.",
        "Meanwhile, the union has demanded that only some petrol stations be given security and that military security be provided as police security is not adequate for the security of petrol stations.",
        "The union also stressed the need for 24-hour security as most petrol stations are prone to collisions."
      ],
